{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"headers"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Regional compliance"}]},{"text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Network monitoring"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Firewall restrictions"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"while preserving all headers and request body content."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"title":"setRevers